---
title: Cheesy BBQ Plant-Based Protein Shred Bowls with Buttery Charred Corn and Rice
description: Bowls are perfect for quick weekday meals and this one will be a hit with the whole family! Protein shreds are tossed in BBQ sauce, then spooned over buttery rice. Charred corn adds some extra comfort to this bowl!
